stories.title: Rain ruins West Indian march
stories.subTitle: Australia v West Indies, VB Series, Brisbane
stories.summary: Brisbane rain spoiled Australia's chances in the inaugural Chappell-Hadlee Trophy in December, but their serious blushes against West Indies were saved by two thunderstorms at the Gabba
